name: Resolve namespace package and pin pyparsing version
body:
* Resolve namespace package (@yifeitao) [#264]
* Update pyparsing requires lock to be more strict [#275]

name: Better substitution resolution and duration support
body:
* Adding the resolve method to resolve substitution keys in 1 config tree with another config tree (@borissmidt) [#266]
* Support serializing timedelta and relativedelta to string (hocon, json etc.) (@gabis-precog) [#263]
* Upgrade to GitHub-native Dependabot (@dependabot-preview) [#260]
* Process substitution overrides in order (@JettJones) [#257]
* Fix duration parsing in lists (@olii) [#255]
* Add support for Python 3.9 and fix deprecation warning (@olii) [#254]

name: Rewrite the logic to resolve package-relative paths so we can remove the "asset" library
Fix self references when environment variables exist (@anujkumar93) [#219]
Fix JSON and HOCON string escaping
Added partial implementation of hocon duration and period recommended api (@gabis-precog) [#199]

body:
* Support conversion of numerically-index objects to arrays (a.1 = 4) (@lune-sta) [#189]
* Handle ConfigValues and ConfigSubstitution in HOCONConverter.to_hocon (@ChristopheDuong) [#192]
* Fix raising of ConfigException for get_int() and get_float() (@ElkMonster) [#188]
* Fixed Flake8 error for Python 2.7

name: Fix incorrect config merge and added backslash escaping
body:
* Escape backslash (@roee-allegro) [#173]
* Fixed incorrect config merge (@aalba6675) [#170]

name: with_fallback and unresolved substitutions
body:
* Added resolve option to with_fallback (@afanasev) [#164]
* Allow unresolved substitution to use default string or substitution string (e.g., ${abc}) [#163]

name: Fixed escaped quotes inside quoted and unquoted string
config merge fixes
body:
* Fix non-root ConfigTree merge onto root ConfigTree (@aalba6675) [#156]
* Unresolved optional substitutions work with config merging (@aalba6675) [#153]

unicode for unquoted strings and compact hocon

Implemented contains method and fixed bug where last line is a comment
Fixed error handling that was unable to deal with unicode keys and Python 2.6 incompatible format string
Bug fix for variables that start with include-blabla
Don't lock pyparsing to a specific version
Fixes for self-reference resolution after merging configs and key with dots
Use recursive merging when concatenating objects
\r and no eol on last line fix
fixed extra space in substitutions and added ConfigTree.merge_configs()
dotted notation fix + default indent of 2
optional substition, include missing file, eol assignment fixes
fixed list of dicts merge and include in lists
fixed bug when None values set explicitly (PR #7)
ConfigTree inherits from OrderedDict and other improvements
added dash and white spaces for keys
substitutions, list concat, string concat, dict concat
added true, false, null support for json, yaml and properties
